{"word":"G591 - ἀποδίδωμι - apodídōmi - ap-od-eed'-o-mee - Deliver","slug":"G591","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποδίδωμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>apodídōmi"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ap-od-eed'-o-mee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Deliver"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B4;&#x03C9;&#x03BC;&#x03B9; - apodido&#x0304;mi</b> - <i>ap-od-eed'-o-mee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G1325\">G1325</a>; to <i>give away</i>, that is, <i>up</i>, <i>over</i>, <i>back</i>, etc. (in various applications): - deliver (again), give (again), (re-) pay (-ment be made), perform, recompense, render, requite, restore, reward, sell, yield,"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1325\">G1325</a>, <a href=\"#/G1431\">G1431</a>, <a href=\"#/G1432\">G1432</a>, <a href=\"#/G1433\">G1433</a>, <a href=\"#/G1434\">G1434</a>, <a href=\"#/G1435\">G1435</a>, <a href=\"#/G3860\">G3860</a>, <a href=\"#/G3862\">G3862</a>, <a href=\"#/G467\">G467</a>, <a href=\"#/G468\">G468</a>, <a href=\"#/G469\">G469</a>"}]}